{"tid":845160,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"二手居屋無人吼！港島3房592尺單位以470萬成交，富榮之後再創新低！","createTime":"2018-10-02T12:21:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-04T10:41:25.000Z","uid":28245,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"38dfeeef225b31fe3031f9304de4fb7d3b55551c","tid":845160,"uid":28245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T12:21:43.000Z","msg":"五二折新居屋及「白居二」夾擊，二手居屋及公屋首當其衝。房委會公佈，9月份全港只錄得38宗居屋第二市場(未補價居屋及公屋)成交，為2002年有紀錄以來新低，並較8月份錄得的77宗再少一半。<br />\n<br />\n柴灣居屋富欣花園2座低層戶，實用面積592方呎，成交價僅470萬元，呎價7,939元，為屋苑3房造價自2016年10月後首次跌穿500萬元。同類3房單位今年4月高位造價582萬元，呎價9,831元，是次低層戶賣平19%或112萬元。<br />\n<br />\n其他區亦有居屋劈價。包括屯門龍門居12座中層D室，實用面積592呎，3房間隔，成交價430萬元，呎價7,264元，與5座中層B室同面積單位今年造價480萬元比較，回落50萬元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181002&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=58748233\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181002%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D58748233&d=MzvXRyIBp%2FgBxpgrfSPzQL%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=26b7a236\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181002%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D58748233&h=dded09ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181002&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=58748233</a> <br />\n【居二成交史上最低】富欣花園3房跌穿5球"},{"pid":"c0771e80f276db5771ac12b31aaabba6c5113871","tid":845160,"uid":52023,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T12:27:32.000Z","msg":"唔"},{"pid":"a2281da7851008b4653cb0c883c585874b73aac0","tid":845160,"uid":28245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T12:27:59.000Z","msg":"計？"},{"pid":"cea8fd509b4d493b8846691f99282daa9af94a3f","tid":845160,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T12:32:15.000Z","msg":"公居將大量供應"},{"pid":"43585f6ce899b221733b775322ab78c7e93a3c99","tid":845160,"uid":137725,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T12:39:52.000Z","msg":"港島不嬲都唔計"}